    <h2>Additonal Benefits of Autopilot</h2>
    <p class="h2-subheadline">We offer two plans. If you have a one-time task, we can pay by the hour. This is what you're you're used to. Some people start with this just to get a sense of our service without commiting. </p>
    

    <h3 class="section-header">Power outages (Is the power out for just us?)</h3>
     <p class="h2-subheadline">Power outages are a regular occurance in Los Angeles. Because we have a network of homes in close proximity, we alert you if the power out is the entire neighborhood or just you. Our system has a backup battery and doesn't depend on wifi, so the system won't fail during an outage. </p>




