  <p class="h2-subheadline">You’re forced to vet strangers, chase down clear pricing, and worry about shoddy work or unfinished jobs. Autopilot changes the game. We accept the responsibility so you don’t have to—handling silent maintenance automatically and unexpected repairs instantly.</p>
  






